Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF A BARRIO IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF RIZAL, PROVINCE OF NUEVA ECIJA, FROM "DELINQUENTE" TO "CORONEL PACO ROMAN."
Data:
[ Acts No. 4092, November 29, 1933 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF A BARRIO IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF RIZAL, PROVINCE OF NUEVA ECIJA, FROM "DELINQUENTE" TO "CORONEL PACO ROMAN."
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines inLegislature assembled and by the authority of the same:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of "Delinquente," in the municipality of Rizal, Province of Nueva Ecija, to all intents and purposes, shall hereafter be known as "Coronel Paco Roman."
Section 2. This Act shall take effect on its approval.1a—àphi1
Approved, November 29, 1933.
